[[File:A_Swarm_of_Ancient_Stars_-_GPN-2000-000930.jpg|thumb]]的[[M80|M80]]距離[[太陽|太陽]]30,000[[光年|光年]]，擁有數十萬顆的恆星<ref>{{cite news
 | author = The Hubble Heritage team
 | url = http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/newsdesk/archive/releases/1999/26/
 | title = Hubble Images a Swarm of Ancient Stars
 | work = HubbleSite News Desk
 | publisher = Space Telescope Science Institute
 | date = 1999-07-01
 | accessdate = 2006-05-26
 | archive-date = 2008-10-07
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081007152325/http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/newsdesk/archive/releases/1999/26/
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。]]
'''球狀星團'''是外觀呈[[球形|球形]]，在[[軌道|軌道]]上繞著[[銀心|星系核心]]運行，很像[[行星|行星]]的恆星集團。球狀星團因為被[[重力|重力]]緊緊束縛，使得恆星高度的向中心集中，因此外觀呈球形。球狀星團被發現多在[[星系|星系]]的[[銀暈|暈]]之中，遠比在星系盤中被發現的[[疏散星團|疏散星團]]擁有更多的恆星，但球狀星團的數量相較疏散星團相對的稀少，在[[銀河系|銀河系]]內迄今只發現150個<ref>{{cite web | last=Harris | first=William E. | date=February 2003 | url=http://www.physics.mcmaster.ca/~harris/mwgc.dat | title=CATALOG OF PARAMETERS FOR MILKY WAY GLOBULAR CLUSTERS: THE DATABASE | accessdate=2009-12-23 | archive-date=2015-05-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507110947/http://www.physics.mcmaster.ca/~harris/mwgc.dat | dead-url=no }}</ref>至158個<ref>{{cite web | last=Frommert | first=Hartmut | date=August 2007 | url=http://spider.seds.org/spider/MWGC/mwgc.html | title=Milky Way Globular Clusters | publisher=SEDS | accessdate=2008-02-26 | archive-date=2015-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150728115248/http://spider.seds.org/spider/MWGC/mwgc.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[銀河系|銀河系]]內也許還有10- 20個或更多個尚未被發現<ref name="milky way">{{cite journal
 | author = Ashman, Keith M.; Zepf, Stephen E.
 | date= 1992
 | title = The formation of globular clusters in merging and interacting galaxies
 | journal = Astrophysical Journal, Part 1
 | volume = 384 | pages = 50–61
 | bibcode = 1992ApJ...384...50A | doi = 10.1086/170850 }}</ref>。這些球狀星團環繞星系公轉的半徑可以達到40,000[[秒差距|秒差距]]（大約130,000[[光年|光年]]）或更遠的距離<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Dauphole, B.; Geffert, M.; Colin, J.; Ducourant, C.; Odenkirchen, M.; Tucholke, H.-J.
 | title=The kinematics of globular clusters, apocentric distances and a halo metallicity gradient
 | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomy-and-astrophysics_1996-09_313_1/page/119
 | journal=[[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | date=1996
 | volume=313 | pages=119–128
 | bibcode=1996A&A...313..119D
 | last2 = Geffert
 | last3 = Colin
 | last4 = Ducourant
 | last5 = Odenkirchen
 | last6 = Tucholke }}</ref>。越大的星系擁有越多：以[[仙女座星系|仙女座星系]]為例，可能有500個球狀星團<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Barmby, P.; Huchra, J. P.
 | title=M31 Globular Clusters in the Hubble Space Telescope Archive. I. Cluster Detection and Completeleness
 | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomical-journal_2001-11_122_5/page/2458
 | journal=The Astronomical Journal | date=2001
 | volume=122 | issue=5 | pages=2458–2468
 | doi = 10.1086/323457 | bibcode=2001AJ....122.2458B|arxiv = astro-ph/0107401 }}</ref>。有些巨大的[[橢圓星系|橢圓星系]]，特別是位於[[星系團|星系團]]中心的，像是[[M87|M87]]<ref>{{cite journal
 | author=McLaughlin, Dean E. ; Harris, William E.; Hanes, David A.
 | title=The spatial structure of the M87 globular cluster system
 | journal=Astrophysical Journal | date=1994
 | volume=422 | issue=2 | pages=486–507
 | bibcode=1994ApJ...422..486M
 | doi=10.1086/173744 }}</ref>，有多達13,000個球狀星團。

在[[本星系群|本星系群]]擁有足夠質量的星系，都有關聯性的球狀星團，並且幾乎每個曾經探測過的大質量星系都被發現擁有球狀星團的系統<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Harris | first = William E.
 | title=Globular cluster systems in galaxies beyond the Local Group
 | journal=Annual Review of Astronomy and Astrophysics
 | date=1991 | volume=29
 | issue = 1 | pages=543–579
 | bibcode=1991ARA&A..29..543H
 | doi=10.1146/annurev.aa.29.090191.002551 }}</ref>。[[人馬座矮橢球星系|人馬座矮橢球星系]]和有 [[大犬座高密度區#爭議|爭議]]的[[大犬座矮星系|大犬座矮星系]]似乎正在將它們的球狀星團（像是[[帕羅馬12|帕羅馬12]]）捐贈給銀河系<ref>{{cite journal
 | author=Dinescu, D. I.; Majewski, S. R.; Girard, T. M.; Cudworth, K. M.
 | title=The Absolute Proper Motion of Palomar 12: A Case for Tidal Capture from the Sagittarius Dwarf Spheroidal Galaxy
 | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomical-journal_2000-10_120_4/page/1892
 | journal=[[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]] | date=2000
 | volume=120 | issue=4 | pages=1892–1905
 | bibcode=2000astro.ph..6314D
 | doi=10.1086/301552 |arxiv = astro-ph/0006314 }}</ref>。這表明這個星系的許多球狀星團在之前是如何取得的。

雖然這些球狀團看起來包含一些最初在銀河系產生的恆星，但它們的[[星系的形成和演化|起源]]和在銀河系演化中扮演的角色仍不清楚。球狀星團看起來和[[矮橢圓星系|矮橢圓星系]]有著顯著的不同，它是母星系形成恆星時的一部分，而不是一個獨立的星系<ref name=apj613>{{cite journal
 | last=Lotz | first=Jennifer M.
 |author2=Miller, Bryan W. |author3=Ferguson, Henry C.
  | title=The Colors of Dwarf Elliptical Galaxy Globular Cluster Systems, Nuclei, and Stellar Halos
 | journal=The Astrophysical Journal
 |date=September 2004 | volume=613
 | issue=1 | pages=262–278 | doi=10.1086/422871 | bibcode=2004ApJ...613..262L|arxiv = astro-ph/0406002 }}</ref>。然而，由天文學家最近的推測顯示，球狀星團和[[矮橢球星系|矮橢球]]可能不能很明確的區分為兩種不同類型的天體<ref name="Bergh2007">{{Cite journal
 | last = van den Bergh | first = Sidney
 | authorlink = Sidney van den Bergh
 | title = Globular Clusters and Dwarf Spheroidal Galaxies
 | date = November 2007
 | journal =[[Monthly_Notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]], in press
 | arxiv=0711.4795
 | doi = 10.1111/j.1745-3933.2008.00424.x
 | volume = 385
 | issue = 1
 | pages = L20
| bibcode=2008MNRAS.385L..20V}}</ref>。

== 觀測簡史 ==
